Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource

Class VersionResource

java.lang.Object
oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.BaseResource
oracle.kubernetes.operator.rest.resource.VersionResource
public class VersionResource
extends BaseResource
VersionResource is a jaxrs resource that implements the REST api for the /operator/{version} path. It can be used to describe a version of the WebLogic operator REST api and to traverse to its child resources.
